data.name: lblPlea.Text
data.value:
Please support your toiling software developer by making a small donation today! Your contribution will keep SLIPS7REAM alive, active, and up-to-date, the way it's been for so many years.
This project has taken months of my life, and the community of users has been helpful and patient, and I'm thankful to every one of you, but without monetary compensation, I will have to work on more profitable projects, and the SLIPS7REAM project will die.
Make a donation today to keep SLIPS7REAM alive!
